<bibRefCitation author="Kondratieff" box="[310,535,367,391]" firstAuthor="Kondratieff" pageId="3" pageNumber="198" pagination="149 - 192" refId="ref1758" refString="Kondratieff, B. C. 2004. Perlodidae - Perlodinae (The Springflies). Pages 149 - 192. In B. P. Stark &amp; B. J. Armitage, editors. Stoneflies (Plecoptera) of Eastern North America. Volume II. Chloroperlidae, Perlidae, and Perlodidae (Perlodinae). The Caddis Press, Columbus, OH, U. S. A., 192 pp." type="book chapter" year="2004">Kondratieff, 2004</bibRefCitation>
). This species was collected recently from a Cumberland Plateau stream in northeastern 
<collectingRegion box="[381,489,438,462]" country="United States of America" name="Alabama" pageId="3" pageNumber="198">Alabama</collectingRegion>
, representing a new state record and a small southern range extension.
</paragraph>
